results.name: Number of new lattice points created at each step in an n X n grid that are not visible.
mathematica: g[n_] := Table[ #^2 &[m], {m, 1, n + 1}] - FoldList[Plus, 1, 2 Array[EulerPhi, n, 2]] - Most[Flatten[ Append[{0}, Table[ #^2 &[m], {m, 1, n + 1}] - FoldList[Plus, 1, 2 Array[EulerPhi, n, 2]]]]]; g[80]
